Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that my son, who's so serious, would go and look at those sorts of magazines...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, it's dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my right hand to continue solving problems, {\alpha&HFF&}I can use my left hand to write down names... and to take out potato chips to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my right hand to continue solving problems, I can use my left hand to write down names... {\alpha&HFF&}and to take out potato chips to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my right hand to continue solving problems, I can use my left hand to write down names... and to take out potato chips to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L himself will be the witness to my alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:36.01,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(361,364)}Contact
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure there's no one following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-{\alpha&HFF&}Hurry!! The withdrawal symptoms... they're--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hurry!! The withdrawal symptoms... they're--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't just making this up so that you can eat your apples, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}I've already circled multiple times, within a 100m radius around you to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I've already circled multiple times, within a 100m radius around you to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but they did mention on the news that there are supposed to be 1,500 more investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just trying to intimidate you, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it yourself; it it was true, they would never have made such a big fuss about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Faster, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you don't treat Shinigami very well, do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that you made me give up eating apples in the house till I'd managed to find all those cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, eat the core as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that I'm definitely going to write your name in my Death Note in the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time to be laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. {\alpha&HFF&}I still have things I need to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I still have things I need to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days ago, a mugger and an embezzler died of heart attacks, {\alpha&HFF&}despite the fact that my family had no knowledge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days ago, a mugger and an embezzler died of heart attacks, despite the fact that my family had no knowledge of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still suspect them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kira can manipulate the time of death, {\alpha&HFF&}they wouldn't be able to kill someone without seeing those broadca---
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kira can manipulate the time of death, they wouldn't be able to kill someone without seeing those broadca---
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to stay silent and pretend to study again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already memorized the locations of all the cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}the only criminals I was able to kill using the potato chips' packet as a cover were a mugger and an embezzler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only criminals I was able to kill using the potato chips' packet as a cover were a mugger and an embezzler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both are quite notably less serious crimes than the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.80,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,And next on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to watch TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.15,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,... are still under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there are criminals dying while I'm not watching TV or using the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll still look suspicious that the lesser criminals only die when I don't appear to be getting any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, {\alpha&HFF&}if I kill some of the lesser criminals while they can see me watching the TV, they'll have no reason to treat those deaths as unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, if I kill some of the lesser criminals while they can see me watching the TV, {\alpha&HFF&}they'll have no reason to treat those deaths as unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, if I kill some of the lesser criminals while they can see me watching the TV, they'll have no reason to treat those deaths as unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, {\alpha&HFF&}regardless of the seriousness of their crimes, I can remember the names and faces of the criminals for when I get out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, regardless of the seriousness of their crimes, {\alpha&HFF&}I can remember the names and faces of the criminals for when I get out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, regardless of the seriousness of their crimes, I can remember the names and faces of the criminals for when I get out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, using the piece of Death Note I keep in my wallet, {\alpha&HFF&}I can scatter their times of death as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, using the piece of Death Note I keep in my wallet, I can scatter their times of death as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My anti-surveillance camera plan is finally complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been over the audio and the video footage from the last five days a countless number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to share my conclusions with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the Kitamura and Yagami households, I observed suspicious behaviour from... {\alpha&HFF&}no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within the Kitamura and Yagami households, I observed suspicious behaviour from... no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remove all the surveillance cameras and bugging devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there weren't any suspects after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to pull ourselves together and start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I actually mean is that, judging by this footage alone, there doesn't appear to be anyone that's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Kira were amongst them, they've done nothing to expose themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, {\alpha&HFF&}they appear to be killing criminals as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, they appear to be killing criminals as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ryuuzaki, do you think that Kira may still be one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I've said before... {\alpha&HFF&}there's a 5% chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I've said before... there's a 5% chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the cameras were up, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira continued to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the cameras were up, Kira continued to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how they're killing people... {\alpha&HFF&}even if they could kill someone by just by wishing for it to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how they're killing people... even if they could kill someone by just by wishing for it to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time that happened, a normal person should react in some way... {\alpha&HFF&}they would reveal it by their expression, or through their behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time that happened, a normal person should react in some way... they would reveal it by their expression, or through their behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira isn't among them".. {\alpha&HFF&}that would be the "normal" conclusion one would draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira isn't among them".. that would be the "normal" conclusion one would draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, {\alpha&HFF&}if Kira is among them, within their own mind, they're already a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, if Kira is among them, {\alpha&HFF&}within their own mind, they're already a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, if Kira is among them, within their own mind, they're already a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill without blinking an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though there is no Kira, but that this is really the work of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way that God requires a name and a face in order to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the work of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some kid who likes to think that they are God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere, out there, a serial killer called "Kira" exists, and I will catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the cameras were to be maintained, I doubt that Kira would exhibit any signs by their behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the best method would be to make them admit that they are Kira and demonstrate how they kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But surely, that's going to be impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light. {\alpha&HFF&}As I thought, the cameras are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light. As I thought, the cameras are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them. The lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light? You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've got ya; {\alpha&HFF&}there may still be bugging devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've got ya; there may still be bugging devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that I'm no longer a target of their investigations, {\alpha&HFF&}although, L will doubtlessly continue to pursue Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that I'm no longer a target of their investigations, although, L will doubtlessly continue to pursue Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}as long as he continues to use the Japanese police force, my father will be in the middle of that investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as long as he continues to use the Japanese police force, {\alpha&HFF&}my father will be in the middle of that investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as long as he continues to use the Japanese police force, my father will be in the middle of that investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... {\alpha&HFF&}I can use my father to reveal L's real identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... I can use my father to reveal L's real identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can erase L... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira will be one step closer to becoming the God of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can erase L... Kira will be one step closer to becoming the God of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, stop making such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relief to know that the bugging devices have also been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that that's one less thing I need to stress about before my exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, getting into university will allow me more time to act as "Kira", {\alpha&HFF&}and the time to go after L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, getting into university will allow me more time to act as "Kira", and the time to go after L.
