Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! {\alpha&HFF&}There's only ten minutes left before the exams starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there! There's only ten minutes left before the exams starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate having to wait around in classrooms, so I was planning to be here three minutes before it starts, but oh well... I managed to arrive earlier than I intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he doesn't lack confidence.
