Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, there's been a load of guys watching the Human World for all they're worth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Ryuk is being kept as a pet by a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What the hell is he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it! He's got no pride as a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was talking about the human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk would make a terrible pet. He's not cute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's his owner like? Female? Male?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might go and take a look myself.
