Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Freshman's speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introducing the freshmen's representative, {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introducing the freshmen's representative, Yagami Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also... {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also... Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuga Hideki... do they mean the idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. {\alpha&HFF&}How is he going to get the grades to get into Toudai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. How is he going to get the grades to get into Toudai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. {\alpha&HFF&}He doesn't look anything like the idol Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. He doesn't look anything like the idol Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that there would be two of us doing this speech... {\alpha&HFF&}but I can't believe it's with him of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that there would be two of us doing this speech... but I can't believe it's with him of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was behind me during the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was sitting in that really odd way that made him stand out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.66,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,New life begins to blossom in the breath of spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the student with the highest grade in the entrance exam usually give this speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:27.29,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally we're able to embrace this bright future...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just means that there were two of them this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.94,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we look forward to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that both of them got top marks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.31,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,...at Toudou University fairness in society will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like that really exist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the one on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kyouko, you're weird... I tell you, normal people would say the one on the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at them though.. {\alpha&HFF&}They're complete opposites!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at them though.. They're complete opposites!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly one looks like a brilliant genius, brought up in a sheltered environment, but... the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:12:00.86,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,New life begins to blossom in the breath of spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could almost call him feral...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he what one would describe as a natural genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing that sort of garb to the entrance ceremony at Toudai, he's either an idiot, or he's mocking the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:14.51,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,...freshmen's representative, Ryuuga Hideki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of police chief, {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Souichirou. You have a sense of justice that matches your father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of police chief, Yagami Souichirou. {\alpha&HFF&}You have a sense of justice that matches your father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The son of police chief, Yagami Souichirou. You have a sense of justice that matches your father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're aiming for a career in the Police Force yourself, {\alpha&HFF&}and in the past you've helped in several cases that have all led to convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're aiming for a career in the Police Force yourself, and in the past you've helped in several cases that have all led to convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, you're interested in the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that sense of justice and ability, {\alpha&HFF&}I could trust you with a very important secret, if you promise not to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that sense of justice and ability, I could trust you with a very important secret, if you promise not to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to tell you something very important regarding the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this? All of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be wiser if I don't talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, {\alpha&HFF&}what's this "important thing" concerning the Kira case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, what's this "important thing" concerning the Kira case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-{\alpha&HFF&}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way L would admit to being L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he seemed a little odd, {\alpha&HFF&}but is he actually crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he seemed a little odd, but is he actually crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Wait. I can't show that I'm uneasy. If he really is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait. {\alpha&HFF&}I can't show that I'm uneasy. If he really is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait. I can't show that I'm uneasy. {\alpha&HFF&}If he really is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait. I can't show that I'm uneasy. If he really is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, right now, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to act as people would expect Yagami Souichirou's son, Yagami Light, to act...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, right now, I've got to act as people would expect Yagami Souichirou's son, Yagami Light, to act...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really are L, then you are someone I admire a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I revealed myself to you because I believe that you might be able to help us with the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light. {\alpha&HFF&}There's only a 5% chance that you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light. There's only a 5% chance that you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But out of all those I watched, there's something about you... {\alpha&HFF&}you're too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But out of all those I watched, there's something about you... you're too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly are Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}this is the best way I can think of to put pressure on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly are Kira, this is the best way I can think of to put pressure on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's L... That's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. {\alpha&HFF&}If this guy really is L... No, even if he isn't, I... I won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. If this guy really is L... {\alpha&HFF&}No, even if he isn't, I... I won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. If this guy really is L... No, {\alpha&HFF&}even if he isn't, I... I won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. If this guy really is L... No, even if he isn't, {\alpha&HFF&}I... I won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. If this guy really is L... No, even if he isn't, I... {\alpha&HFF&}I won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. If this guy really is L... No, even if he isn't, I... I {\alpha&HFF&}won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. If this guy really is L... No, even if he isn't, I... I won't be able to do anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's L, {\alpha&HFF&}then my father would know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's L, then my father would know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he dies after telling me that he's L, I'll immediately become the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, this guy is using the blatantly fake name "Ryuuga Hideki".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to kill him by writing that name in the Death Note, {\alpha&HFF&}then if his real name isn't Ryuuga Hideki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I try to kill him by writing that name in the Death Note, then if his real name isn't Ryuuga Hideki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idol Ryuuga may die instead, as his face instinctively appears in my mind when I think of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.93,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs73.220339\frx44\fry350\frz8.241\pos(312,138)\fad(0,500)\c&HA9A9A4&\3c&H000000&}Ryuuga Hideki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without dying himself, he'll be able to tell whether I'm Kira or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he L? {\alpha&HFF&}And does he suspect that I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he L? And does he suspect that I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell to what extent he suspects me, but I'm sure he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other reason to reveal himself to the son of Yagami Souichirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this indicate that he's still investigating those who were previously being investigated by Ray Penber?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}why is L here, in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why is L here, in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be thinking about this right now. {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to exhibit a cool demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be thinking about this right now. I've got to exhibit a cool demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely watching me for a reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That entrance ceremony was fun, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light. That guy's calling ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A limousine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll see you on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His family is probably loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a top student as well. That's kind of creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Toudai student!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!! He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, L! {\alpha&HFF&}I've never been so humiliated in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, L! I've never been so humiliated in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. {\alpha&HFF&}Hey, you could always just do the trade for the eyes of a Shinigami and kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. Hey, {\alpha&HFF&}you could always just do the trade for the eyes of a Shinigami and kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. Hey, you could always just do the trade for the eyes of a Shinigami and kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if this whole thing turns out to be a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I kill him, and it turns out that he isn't L, it'll be as good as telling the real L that I am Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami killing a human isn't the same as a human killing a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kill him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I kill him, they'll trace it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note can only kill the person whose name is written down, {\alpha&HFF&}I can't manipulate others into killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note can only kill the person whose name is written down, I can't manipulate others into killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death note is so inconvenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always so calm, but he finally flipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first I thought that I'd only need his name and then I'd be able to kill him via an accident or suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}unless I'm 100% sure that he's the real L, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, unless I'm 100% sure that he's the real L, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}even if he is the real L, the fact that he's already told me might mean that it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if he is the real L, {\alpha&HFF&}the fact that he's already told me might mean that it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if he is the real L, the fact that he's already told me might mean that it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how he dies, {\alpha&HFF&}the police will be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how he dies, the police will be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never have thought that he would reveal himself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those individuals who he suspects of being Kira... he doesn't have to worry about them, even if he's a substitute for L... {\alpha&HFF&}he only needs to introduce himself to them as L...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those individuals who he suspects of being Kira... he doesn't have to worry about them, even if he's a substitute for L... he only needs to introduce himself to them as L...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For L, this is an extremely effective defence against Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}and it's also a form of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For L, this is an extremely effective defence against Kira... and it's also a form of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me. {\alpha&HFF&}It was an excellent move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me. It was an excellent move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga might have pretended that he had no ulterior motives, {\alpha&HFF&}but he'll try and get close to me through university and try to manipulate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga might have pretended that he had no ulterior motives, but he'll try and get close to me through university, {\alpha&HFF&}and try to manipulate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuga might have pretended that he had no ulterior motives, but he'll try and get close to me through university, and try to manipulate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing to get depressed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just proves that L has nothing to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is now a straight-forward competition of bluffing and knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface, {\alpha&HFF&}it looks like we're "best friends", but in reality, we're both trying to find out whether the other is "L" or "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface, it looks like we're "best friends", but in reality, we're both trying to find out whether the other is "L" or "Kira".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. {\alpha&HFF&}I would never have imagined that you would come, offering me friendship, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. I would never have imagined that you would come, offering me friendship, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wholeheartedly accept your friendship, make you believe me, make you divulge all your information, and then kill you... Without fail.
